def solution(a, b, n):
    ans = 0
    for _ in range(1,n + 1):
        toss = a * b
        ans += toss
        a += 1
        b += 1
    return(ans)

You are standing at a magical well. 
It has two positive integers written on it: a and b. 
Each time you cast a magic marble into the well, it gives you a * b dollars 
then both a and b increase by 1. 
You have n magic marbles. How much money will you make?
